Method.ЗаменитьСсылки.Return.Description=* ObektOshibki - Arbitrary - Object - prichina Flag.\n* PredstavlenieObektaOshibki - String - strokovoe Presentation Form Flag.\n* TipOshibki - String - Type Flag\:\n"OshibkaBlokirovki"  - On Info References nekotorye Objects byli zablokirovany.\n"DannyeIzmeneny"    - In protsesse Data processors Data byli izmeneny drugim User.\n"OshibkaZapisi"      - Dont smogli Write Object, Or Method VozmozhnostZamenyElementov vernul otkaz.\n"OshibkaUdaleniya"    - Dont smogli Delete Object.\n"NeizvestnyeDannye" - On Info byli naydeny Data, kotorye Dont planirovalis S analizu, Replacement Dont realizovana.\n* TekstOshibki - String - podrobnoe Description Flag.
