Method.ХранилищеНастроекДанныхФормЗагрузить.Description=Zagruzhaet Result From Storage Manager Schema Form, As Method Platform Import,\nobektov StandartnoeKhranilishcheNastroekMenedzher Or KhranilishcheNastroekMenedzher.<Name Storage>,\nno C podderzhkoy dliny Key Manager bolee 128 Symbols putem kheshirovaniya Parts,\nkotoraya prevyshaet 96 Symbols.\nKrome togo, vozvrashchaet ukazannoe Value By Default, If Settings Dont naydeny.\nEsli Objects Tools SokhranenieDannykhPolzovatelya, vozvrashchaetsya Value By Default Debug Flag.\nV vozvrashchaemom znachenii ochishchayutsya References To nesushchestvuyushchiy Object In Base Schema, A imenno\n- vozvrashchaemaya Ref zamenyaetsya To ukazannoe Value By Default;\n- From Schema Type Array References udalyayutsya;\n- U Schema Type Structure T Type Key Dont menyaetsya, A Value ustanavlivaetsya Neopredeleno;\n- analiz Table In Schema Type Array, Structure, Type vypolnyaetsya Recursively.
